Type: Package
Package: rfm
Title: Recency, Frequency and Monetary Value Analysis
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person("Aravind", "Hebbali", email = "hebbali.aravind@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for RFM (recency, frequency and monetary) analysis. Generate 
    RFM score, heatmap for average monetary value for different recency and 
    frequency scores, histograms of scores, examine the distribution of monetary 
    score for the different combinations of frequency and recency scores, 
    scatter plots for examining the relationship between the scores.
